Interface IComponent<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - type of the identifier.
    All Superinterfaces:
    IdProvider<K>, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IdComponent, NullComponent, RevisionDocument, SnomedComponentDocument, SnomedConceptDocument, SnomedConstraintDocument, SnomedDescriptionIndexEntry, SnomedDocument, SnomedRefSetMemberIndexEntry, SnomedRelationshipIndexEntry

    public interface IComponent<K>
extends IdProvider<K>, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a terminology independent component with a unique identifier and a human readable label.

    The following features are supported:

    • Retrieve the identifier
    • Retrieve the component label
